                [ a oc:Section ;
                    oc:hasSubsection [ a oc:Section ;
                            oc:hasContent [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                                    oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                                    oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                                    oc:textContent "The most effective Skill development process involves Claude itself. Work with one instance of Claude (\"Claude A\") to create a Skill that will be used by other instances (\"Claude B\"). Claude A helps you design and refine instructions, while Claude B tests them in real tasks. This works because Claude models understand both how to write effective agent instructions and what information agents need." ],
                                [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                                    oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                                    oc:contentOrder 5 ;
                                    oc:textContent "The same hierarchical pattern continues when improving Skills. You alternate between:" ],
                                [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                                    oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                                    oc:contentOrder 2 ;
                                    oc:textContent "**Creating a new Skill:**" ],
                                [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                                    oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                                    oc:contentOrder 4 ;
                                    oc:textContent "**Iterating on existing Skills:**" ],
                                _:ref_80e20b73cb744d3e,
                                [ a oc:BulletList ;
                                    oc:blockType "bullet_list" ;
                                    oc:contentOrder 6 ;
                                    oc:hasItem [ a oc:BulletItem ;
                                            oc:blockType "bullet_item" ;
                                            oc:itemOrder 1 ;
                                            oc:itemText "**Working with Claude A** (the expert who helps refine the Skill)" ],
                                        [ a oc:BulletItem ;
                                            oc:blockType "bullet_item" ;
                                            oc:itemOrder 3 ;
                                            oc:itemText "**Observing Claude B's behavior** and bringing insights back to Claude A" ],
                                        [ a oc:BulletItem ;
                                            oc:blockType "bullet_item" ;
                                            oc:itemOrder 2 ;
                                            oc:itemText "**Testing with Claude B** (the agent using the Skill to perform real work)" ] ],
                                _:ref_9e9f4fbb6993ab85,
                                _:ref_be4b598d025a2c4a,
                                [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                                    oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                                    oc:contentOrder 10 ;
                                    oc:textContent "**Why this approach works**: Claude A understands agent needs, you provide domain expertise, Claude B reveals gaps through real usage, and iterative refinement improves Skills based on observed behavior rather than assumptions." ],
                                [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                                    oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                                    oc:contentOrder 8 ;
                                    oc:textContent "**Gathering team feedback:**" ] ;
                            oc:sectionLevel 3 ;
                            oc:sectionOrder 28 ;
                            oc:sectionTitle "Develop Skills iteratively with Claude" ],
                        [ a oc:Section ;
                            oc:hasContent [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                                    oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                                    oc:contentOrder 3 ;
                                    oc:textContent "Iterate based on these observations rather than assumptions. The 'name' and 'description' in your Skill's metadata are particularly critical. Claude uses these when deciding whether to trigger the Skill in response to the current task. Make sure they clearly describe what the Skill does and when it should be used." ],
                                [ a oc:BulletList ;
                                    oc:blockType "bullet_list" ;
                                    oc:contentOrder 2 ;
                                    oc:hasItem [ a oc:BulletItem ;
                                            oc:blockType "bullet_item" ;
                                            oc:itemOrder 3 ;
                                            oc:itemText "**Overreliance on certain sections**: If Claude repeatedly reads the same file, consider whether that content should be in the main SKILL.md instead" ],
                                        [ a oc:BulletItem ;
                                            oc:blockType "bullet_item" ;
                                            oc:itemOrder 4 ;
                                            oc:itemText "**Ignored content**: If Claude never accesses a bundled file, it might be unnecessary or poorly signaled in the main instructions" ],
                                        [ a oc:BulletItem ;
                                            oc:blockType "bullet_item" ;
                                            oc:itemOrder 1 ;
                                            oc:itemText "**Unexpected exploration paths**: Does Claude read files in an order you didn't anticipate? This might indicate your structure isn't as intuitive as you thought" ],
                                        [ a oc:BulletItem ;
                                            oc:blockType "bullet_item" ;
                                            oc:itemOrder 2 ;
                                            oc:itemText "**Missed connections**: Does Claude fail to follow references to important files? Your links might need to be more explicit or prominent" ] ],
                                [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                                    oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                                    oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                                    oc:textContent "As you iterate on Skills, pay attention to how Claude actually uses them in practice. Watch for:" ] ;
                            oc:sectionLevel 3 ;
                            oc:sectionOrder 29 ;
                            oc:sectionTitle "Observe how Claude navigates Skills" ],
                        [ a oc:Section ;
                            oc:hasContent _:ref_0e90ec8071262299,
