_:ref_2c46ea57820c2eeb a oc:WorkflowStep ;
    dcterms:description "**Complete a task without a Skill**: Work through a problem with Claude A using normal prompting. As you work, you'll naturally provide context, explain preferences, and share procedural knowledge. Notice what information you repeatedly provide." ;
